 Nia Archives 发行新单曲“Bad Gyalz”并宣布举办日狂欢https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-releases-new-single-bad-gyalz-and-announces-day-rave-3477829?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nia-archives-releases-新单曲坏加兹并宣布狂欢日Emma WilkesThu, 03 Aug 2023 16:40:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsJungleradarRaphttps://www.nme.com/?p=3477829 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼亚档案馆" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “每当我去看一场演出时，85% 的观众都是 18 -25 岁的女性，这太神奇了！”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-releases-new-single-bad-gyalz-and-announces-day-rave-3477829">Nia Archives 发布新单曲“Bad Gyalz”并宣布 Day rave</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼亚档案馆" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/nia-archive-scott-dudelson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a>分享了一首新单曲“Bad Gyalz”，并宣布举办一天狂欢。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-sunrise-bang-ur-head-against-the-wall-ep-review-radar-3410198">Nia Archives – “Sunrise Bang Ur Head Against Tha Wall”EP 评论：诚实的故事和柔和的节奏</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌是艺术家自 6 月份的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-flips-heads-will-roll-on-spooky-new-song-off-wiv-ya-headz-3454149">《Off Wiv Ya Headz》</a>以来首张新专辑，其中插入了 A-Trak 的大型版本<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yeah-yeah-yeahs">Yeah Yeah Yeahs</a>的《Heads Will Roll》。</p><p>谈到这首歌，Archives 说道：“我和 Clipz 一起去录音室，听 Ranking Ann 的歌，她是我最喜欢的 MC 之一。就这样。然后我就在想这样一个事实，就像每当我去看一场演出时，85% 的女性都在 18 -25 岁之间，这真是太神奇了！他们都是坏人，绝对的丛林主义者。所以我想创作一首代表这一点以及参加狂欢节的女性的歌曲。 Bad Gyalz 就这样诞生了！”</p><p>该视频是用 VHS 拍摄的，其中有一些来自各行各业的不同女孩与朋友一起出去玩的片段。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a> 、Buck Betty、PXSSY PALACE 等人的客串。</p><p>看看下面的“Bad Gyalz”： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nia Archives - Bad Gyalz（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oEIHBnmCAr0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>为了庆祝这首歌的发行，Archives 宣布将于本周六（8 月 6 日）在伦敦码头路 60 号为女性、非二元性别人士和 LGBTQ+ 群体成员举办一场一次性的“Bad Gyalz Day Party”。这场狂欢将有来自 DJ Flight、PXSSY PALACE、Sim0ne、Izzy Bossy 等的 DJ 表演。</p><p> Archives 今年早些时候发行了一张新 EP“Sunrise Bang Ur Head Against Tha Wall”。 <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-sunrise-bang-ur-head-against-the-wall-ep-review-radar-3410198">四星评论</a>中写道：“像高辛烷值的巴萨诺瓦重制版《Baianá》和崇高的同名曲目让她的制作技巧脱颖而出，但真正让这张 EP 成为焦点的是她的歌曲创作。不再依赖节拍来让你动起来，它柔和的感觉让你坐下来听 Nia 的故事，看到她编曲的曲子背后的人。</p><p> “能够在职业生涯的早期表现出如此多的人性和多才多艺，这是非常值得尊敬的，如果这是对未来的一瞥，那么 Nia Archives 看起来将成为不可阻挡的一代人才。”</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-releases-new-single-bad-gyalz-and-announces-day-rave-3477829">Nia Archives 发布新单曲“Bad Gyalz”并宣布 Day rave</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
威尔·史密斯表示，成名后“家里没有人感到高兴” https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-says-nobody-in-my-family-was-happy-after-achiving-fame-3477846?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=will-smith-说我家里没有人在成名后感到高兴Chris EdwardsThu, 03 Aug 2023 16:07:52 +0000 Film NewsNewsWill Smith https://www.nme.com/?p=3477846 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “物质条件并不等于幸福”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-says-nobody-in-my-family-was-happy-after-achieving-fame-3477846">威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith) 在成名后表示“我家里没有人感到高兴”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯</a>公开讲述了他的家人在成功初期所感受到的不幸。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>获奖演员因 NBC 情景喜剧<em>《新鲜贝莱尔王子》而</em>声名鹊起，该剧于 1990 年至 1996 年播出。</p><p>然而，直到二十年后，当他的两个孩子贾登和威洛经历了自己的成功时，史密斯才觉得自己实现了自己的梦想。</p><p> “2010 年对于艺术家和家长来说都是最伟大的一年，”史密斯在凯文·哈特 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-hart">Kevin Hart</a> ) 的孔雀电视节目《心心相印》 <em>(Hart To Heart)</em>第三季大结局中承认。</p><p> “《<em>空手道小子》</em>于 6 月推出，《鞭打我的头发》于 10 月推出，”<em>理查德国王</em>演员说道，指的是贾登的第一部主要电影和威洛的首张首张单曲。</p><p> “我正在建立一个我心中的家庭梦想。 “我会比我父亲做得更好。”我们已经讨论过了，我父亲经常虐待我。我告诉自己，我永远不会对我的家人有那样的能量，我有一个梦想，一个我正在建立的家庭的想法。几乎从 2010 年到 2012 年，我已经实现了我梦想的一切。” </p><figure id="attachment_3115260" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3115260" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3115260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith.jpg" alt="威洛·史密斯和贾登·史密斯" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Willow-and-Jaden-Smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3115260" class="wp-caption-text">威洛·史密斯和贾登·史密斯。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>然而，尽管史密斯和他的家人取得了成功，但他回忆说“我家里没有人感到高兴”。</p><p> “没有人想加入一个排。威洛是第一个开始叛变的人，这是我第一次意识到成功和金钱并不意味着幸福，”这位演员说。</p><p> “在那之前，我真的相信你可以成功——拥有房子和家庭——并且你可以赢得幸福。”</p><p><em>这位黑衣人</em>明星说，就在那时，他意识到“物质条件并不等于幸福，在很多情况下，它们可能是你不幸福的原因”。</p><p> “你可以拥有太多的东西，这会让你感到痛苦，”史密斯补充道。 “那是我第一次撤退，我想，‘好吧，我错过了什么？’我以一种在我周围留下焦土的方式驱赶着我周围的人。”</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-hollywood-actors-strike-pivotal-moment-for-our-profession-3476622">史密斯最近分享了他对正在进行的好莱坞演员罢工的看法</a>，并将其描述为“我们职业的关键时刻”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-says-nobody-in-my-family-was-happy-after-achieving-fame-3477846">威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith) 在成名后表示“我家里没有人感到高兴”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 88Rising 与本田合作为突破艺术家提供机会https://www.nme.com/news/music/88rising-partner-with-honda-to-offer-opportunities-to-writing-artists-3477837?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=88rising-partner-with-honda-为突破艺术家提供机会Liberty DunworthThu, 03 Aug 2023 15:55:14 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3477837 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="本田 X 88rising 服装系列 2023 &#39;88 Type R&#39;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两人还联手推出了新的服装系列</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/88rising-partner-with-honda-to-offer-opportunities-to-breaking-artists-3477837">88Rising 与 Honda 合作，为新锐艺术家提供机会，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="本田 X 88rising 服装系列 2023 &#39;88 Type R&#39;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising-press@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/88rising">88Rising</a>宣布与本田联手为新兴人才提供机会。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/head-in-the-clouds-new-york-review-88rising-comes-home-3446792">Head In The Clouds 纽约评论：88rising 在全球跳跃音乐节上以时尚方式回家</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>该品牌是一家全球音乐和媒体公司，致力于代表美国最优秀的亚洲人才，并为突破性艺术家提供更大的平台来追求他们的职业生涯。</p><p>现在，88Rising已确认与本田建立合作伙伴关系，为粉丝创造更多难忘的音乐体验，并继续支持亚洲新兴艺术家。</p><p>两人希望实现这一目标的方式之一是参加今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/head-in-the-clouds-new-york-review-88rising-comes-home-3446792">Head in the Clouds 音乐艺术节</a>，该节由 88Rising 组织，将于 8 月 5 日至 6 日在加利福尼亚州帕萨迪纳举行。</p><p>在这里，参加者将享受组织的“独特体验和史诗般的表演”，并观看包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/artists/stephanie-poetri">Stephanie Poetri</a> 、Spence Lee、Lyn Lapid、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/artists/phum-viphurit">Phum Viphurit</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eyedress">Eyedress</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/grentperez">Grentperez</a>和 Akini Jing 在内的艺术家的表演——所有这些都将在新本田红双喜舞台。</p><p>作为 Head in the Clouds 的官方汽车合作伙伴，“88 Type R Honda Customs Shop”节日活动是“对改装车车库的独特诠释，其中包括一辆 2000 Civic Si 项目车和全新 2023 Honda Civic Type R –有史以来在美国销售的最强大的本田量产车”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3446810" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3446810" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3446810" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew.jpg" alt="纽约云端" width="2000" height="1271" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/hitc-ny-Rich-Brian-dillonmatthew-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3446810" class="wp-caption-text">纽约 Head in the Clouds 的 Rich Brian。图片来源：迪里安·马修</figcaption></figure><p>本田与 88rising 首次服装合作的细节也已分享。该系列名为“88 Type R”，将在 Head In The Clouds 音乐节上亮相，并在 88nightmarket 在线发售。</p><p>所提供的服装将完全男女皆宜，其中包括灵感来自 90 年代末至 00 年代初亚洲汽车文化的剪裁单品。</p><p>本田于 2022 年开始与 88rising 合作，推出了全新 HR-V 紧凑型 SUV。两个品牌还发布了由 88rising 印尼创作歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niki">NIKI</a> 、印尼说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warren-hue">Warren Hue</a>和美籍华裔独立艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mxmtoon">mxmtoon</a>主演的纪录片系列，分享每位艺术家的职业生涯以及他们一路上面临的挑战。</p><p>谈及此次合作，本田营销媒体部负责人 Phillip Lee 表示：“本田对音乐和年轻突破艺术家的支持已有二十多年，我们与 88rising 的合作将让他们的想象力和决心的故事得以表达。” </p><figure id="attachment_3477841" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477841" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477841" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270.jpg" alt="本田 X 88rising 服装系列 2023 &#39;88 Type R&#39;" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Honda-88rising@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477841" class="wp-caption-text">本田 X 88rising 服装系列 2023 &#39;88 Type R&#39;。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“88rising 提升并赋予亚洲艺术家权力，本田很自豪能够提供一个平台来帮助支持他们的梦想并推进他们的职业生涯。”</p><p><a href="https://88rising.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关合作伙伴关系的更多信息，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fhead-in-the-clouds-tickets%2Fartist%2FZ7r9jZak5d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找 Head In The Clouds 音乐节的门票。</p><p>早在五月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/head-in-the-clouds-new-york-review-88rising-comes-home-3446792"><em>《NME》</em>就给了纽约版《Head In The Clouds》四星评价</a>，并称赞其有能力举办“一场充满乐趣的节日，庆祝亚洲侨民的音乐、文化和美食”。</p><p> “周六，一场倾盆大雨可能会浇灭 HITC 的士气，但相反，似乎只会让观众更加兴奋——我们从新泽西一路前往雅加达，” <em>NME</em>的 Rhian Daly 写道。</p><p> “说唱歌手 Spence Lee 跨越哈德逊河，在双喜舞台上表演了一场被雨水浸湿的演出，让一群披着防水斗篷的人随着《On God》轻松的节奏一起摇摆。随后，在同一舞台上，圣地亚哥制作人 ISOxo 将他面前的混凝土空间变成了挥舞拳头的电动狂欢场。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/88rising-partner-with-honda-to-offer-opportunities-to-breaking-artists-3477837">88Rising 与 Honda 合作，为新锐艺术家提供机会，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
